{# Tenant Defense Statement - English #}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Tenant Defense Statement</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; margin: 40px; }
        .header { text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid black; padding-bottom: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .section { margin: 20px 0; }
        .section-title { font-weight: bold; background: #f0f0f0; padding: 8px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        p { margin: 5px 0; font-size: 11px; }
        .disclaimer { font-size: 9px; border: 1px solid #999; padding: 8px; background: #fffacd; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
    <h1>WRITTEN STATEMENT IN DEFENSE</h1>
    <h2>Tenant Eviction Case</h2>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">PARTIES:</div>
    <p><strong>Plaintiff:</strong> {{ landlord_name }}</p>
    <p><strong>Respondent (Tenant):</strong> {{ tenant_name }}</p>
    <p><strong>Case No.:</strong> {{ case_number }}</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">PROPERTY DETAILS:</div>
    <p><strong>Property Address:</strong> {{ property_address }}</p>
    <p><strong>Type:</strong> {{ property_type }}</p>
    <p><strong>Rent Amount:</strong> ₹{{ rent_amount }} per month</p>
    <p><strong>Tenancy Start Date:</strong> {{ tenancy_start_date }}</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">GROUNDS OF DEFENSE:</div>
    <p><strong>1. Regular Payment of Rent:</strong></p>
    <p style="margin-left: 20px;">The respondent has paid rent regularly as per the agreement. 
    Bank statements and payment receipts are attached as evidence.</p>
    
    <p><strong>2. No Breach of Terms:</strong></p>
    <p style="margin-left: 20px;">The respondent has complied with all conditions of the tenancy agreement.</p>
    
    <p><strong>3. Inadequate Notice:</strong></p>
    <p style="margin-left: 20px;">The notice period given is insufficient. Under the Residential Tenancy Act, 
    a minimum of 3 months' notice is required for eviction, not {{ notice_period_days }} days.</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">PRAYER:</div>
    <p>It is therefore respectfully prayed that:</p>
    <p>1. The suit be dismissed with costs.</p>
    <p>2. Respondent be allowed to continue in occupation of the premises.</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <p><strong>I declare that the above information is true to the best of my knowledge.</strong></p>
    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">_____________________________</p>
    <p>{{ tenant_name }}</p>
    <p>Date: {{ date_of_statement }}</p>
</div>

<div class="disclaimer">
    <p><strong>DISCLAIMER:</strong> This template is for informational purposes. Different states have different rent laws. 
    Please consult a local lawyer for specific guidance on your case. This is not legal advice.</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
